- Señor.

505
00:30:07,261 --> 00:30:08,426
Señor...

506
00:30:08,496 --> 00:30:10,396
...si me permite...

507
00:30:10,498 --> 00:30:12,432
...creo que quizá hayamos hallado
una solución...

508
00:30:12,500 --> 00:30:15,492
...al problemita económico de Sam.

509
00:30:15,570 --> 00:30:17,435
¿Una solución?

510
00:30:17,505 --> 00:30:19,530
Sí. Un empleo.

511
00:30:19,607 --> 00:30:21,575
¿Un empleo?

512
00:30:23,511 --> 00:30:26,444
